Name "EMC Loop"

Every Redstone Pulse Do

        Input 1028
            arcanium
            From Source

        Output Retain 1028
            arcanium
            To CrafterEMC

Forget

        Input 512
            projecte:*
            From CrafterEMC Slots 26, 27, 28, 29

        Output 512
            projecte:*
            To Source

End
